div.h1: PIC Remapping: IRQ to Vector Mapping

div.p: IRQ0 Vector 32 IRQ1 Vector 33 ... IRQ8 Vector 40
The 8259A PIC defaults to mapping IRQ0-7 to vectors 8-15, which conflicts with CPU exceptions (Double Fault at 8, GPF at 13, etc.).
Remapping moves IRQs to vectors 32-47, leaving 0-31 for CPU exceptions.
